{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyView"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds a shadow to this view."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"shadow","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"color","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Color","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore5ColorV"},{"text":" = Color(.sRGBLinear, white: 0, opacity: 0.33), ","kind":"text"},{"text":"radius","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"x","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV"},{"text":" = 0, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"y","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV"},{"text":" = 0) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The shadow’s color.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"color"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A measure of how much to blur the shadow. Larger values"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"result in more blur."}]}],"name":"radius"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An amount to offset the shadow horizontally from the view.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"x"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An amount to offset the shadow vertically from the view."}]}],"name":"y"}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that adds a shadow to this view."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier to add a shadow of a specified color behind a view."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You can offset the shadow from its view independently in the horizontal"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and vertical dimensions using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"x"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"y"},{"type":"text","text":" parameters. You can also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"blur the edges of the shadow using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"radius"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter. Use a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"radius of zero to create a sharp shadow. Larger radius values produce"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"softer shadows."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The example below creates a grid of boxes with varying offsets and blur."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Each box displays its radius and offset values for reference."}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["struct Shadow: View {","    let steps = [0, 5, 10]","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            ForEach(steps, id: \\.self) { offset in","                HStack(spacing: 50) {","                    ForEach(steps, id: \\.self) { radius in","                        Color.blue","                            .shadow(","                                color: .primary,","                                radius: CGFloat(radius),","                                x: CGFloat(offset), y: CGFloat(offset))","                            .overlay {","                                VStack {","                                    Text(\"\\(radius)\")","                                    Text(\"(\\(offset), \\(offset))\")","                                }","                            }","                    }","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The example above uses "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color\/primary"},{"type":"text","text":" as the color to make the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shadow easy to see for the purpose of illustration. In practice,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you might prefer something more subtle, like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Color\/gray-8j2b"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you don’t specify a color, the method uses a semi-transparent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"black."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyView\/shadow(color:radius:x:y:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/anyview\/shadow(color:radius:x:y:)"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"metadata":{"extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"title":"shadow(color:radius:x:y:)","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text